  EffectDiscription_JPN: 
  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[Hand] [Main] If you have [Shoto Kazama], by placing 1
    [Galemon] from your trash as any of your [Pteromon]'s bottom digivolution card,
    it digivolves into this card for a digivolution cost of 3, ignoring digivolution
    requirements.\n[When Digivolving] You may suspend 1 Digimon. Then, you may play
    1 3000 DP or lower green Digimon card with [Avian] or [Bird]\_in any of its traits
    from your hand without paying the cost. For each suspended Digimon, add 1000
    to this effect's DP maximum."
  InheritedEffectDiscription_JPN: 
  InheritedEffectDiscription_ENG: "[Your Turn] [Once Per Turn] When this Digimon
    wins a battle, this [Vortex Warriors]\_trait Digimon may unsuspend."
